descriptionHTML:
AQUAPIXEL features 3 minimalistic analog watchfaces with a watercolor painted backgrounds from the French Artist EmeMms. This watchface pack is optimised for Round watches like the Moto 360 and the LG G Watch R/Urbane.

Currently there a 3 Analog watchfaces but there will be more in the near future with more customisation ( colors and digital/analog styles)

If you like EmeMms's work you can :

Buy real size prints on Etsy: https://www.etsy.com/fr/shop/EmeMms
